| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3305 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4ac5847f-0ad3-55c9-95f5-0cd9c4246928"
